In [7]:
fullData2017 = pd.read_csv('valeursfoncieres-2017.txt', sep='|')
columns_to_keep = ['Date mutation','Nature mutation','Valeur fonciere','Code postal','Commune','Code departement','Code commune','Nombre de lots','Code type local','Type local','Surface reelle bati','Nombre pieces principales','Surface terrain']
fullData2017['Date mutation'] = pd.to_datetime(fullData2017['Date mutation'])
fullData2017['Code departement'] = fullData2017['Code departement'].astype(str)
fullData2017 = fullData2017[columns_to_keep]
fullData2017 = fullData2017.dropna()
fullData2017['Valeur fonciere'] = pd.to_numeric(fullData2017['Valeur fonciere'].str.replace(',', '.'))
